00:10:26,886 --> 00:10:30,423
AND THE GOOD NEWS IS,
KEVIN IS HAPPY TO COME IN,

00:10:30,423 --> 00:10:33,426
SO OUR OFFER COMBINED IS

00:10:33,426 --> 00:10:36,196
$300,000
FOR 51% OF THE BUSINESS,

00:10:36,196 --> 00:10:39,199
BECAUSE I THINK
THAT'S REALLY KEY TO ME,

00:10:39,199 --> 00:10:41,100
TO MAINTAIN CONTROL.

00:10:41,100 --> 00:10:43,102
WELL, AGAIN, I DON'T THINK

00:10:43,102 --> 00:10:45,171
THAT YOU FULLY UNDERSTAND
OUR BUSINESS.

00:10:45,171 --> 00:10:48,141
WAIT. DON'T SAY THAT.
<i>I</i> KNOW YOUR BUSINESS.

00:10:48,141 --> 00:10:51,110
DO YOU KNOW ANYBODY ELSE
IN YOUR SPHERE OF CONTACTS

00:10:51,110 --> 00:10:54,314
THAT'S EVER SOLD AN EDUCATIONAL
BUSINESS FOR OVER $3 BILLION?

00:10:54,314 --> 00:10:56,583
DO YOU?
WE DO NOT.

00:10:56,583 --> 00:10:59,786
(Robert) SO, BABZ, YOUR‐‐
YOU'RE LOOKING AT ONE
RIGHT HERE.

00:10:59,786 --> 00:11:01,821
WE CAN ARGUE ABOUT THIS
ALL DAY LONG.

00:11:01,821 --> 00:11:05,792
ARE THESE GUYS
GONNA GIVE YOU AN ANSWER?
WHAT WAS
YOUR ANSWER, BABZ?

00:11:05,792 --> 00:11:07,460
(O'Leary) WHAT DO YOU SAY?

00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:09,829
RESPECTFULLY, WE'D LIKE
TO COUNTEROFFER, UM, AT 20%.

00:11:09,829 --> 00:11:13,066
51% OF OUR BUSINESS, UM,
AFTER WHAT WE'VE PUT INTO IT

00:11:13,066 --> 00:11:15,068
AND WHERE WE ARE
AFTER FIVE YEARS,

00:11:15,068 --> 00:11:17,837
I DON'T THINK
IS A FAIR OFFER.
WE ARE NOT WILLING
TO GIVE THAT UP.

00:11:17,837 --> 00:11:20,840
SO YOUR‐‐YOUR COUNTEROFFER
IS WHAT?
20%.

00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:22,842
FOR $300,000?
CORRECT.

00:11:22,842 --> 00:11:27,347
SO YOU THINK THAT THE BUSINESS
IS WORTH $1.5 MILLION TODAY?

00:11:27,347 --> 00:11:30,283
WE THINK IT'S WORTH $3 MILLION,
BUT WE'D LIKE TO WORK WITH YOU

00:11:30,283 --> 00:11:33,453
AND‐‐
IT'S NOT WORTH $3 MILLION,
NOT IN TODAY'S WORLD.

00:11:33,453 --> 00:11:36,089
WELL,
THAT'S WHERE WE DISAGREE.

00:11:40,226 --> 00:11:42,195
THE RISK IS TOO HIGH.

00:11:42,195 --> 00:11:46,065
I CAN'T SEE HOW
I'D GET MY MONEY BACK AT 20%.

00:11:46,065 --> 00:11:48,601
I STICK TO MY ORIGINAL OFFER.
NO?

00:11:48,601 --> 00:11:51,437
NO, THANK YOU.
NO, NOT EVEN CLOSE.

00:11:51,437 --> 00:11:52,772
(Babz chuckles)

00:11:52,772 --> 00:11:55,074
NOT EVEN MAYBE.
(O'Leary) YOU KNOW‐‐

00:11:55,074 --> 00:11:58,144
WELL, I'M‐‐I'M OUT.
OVER TO YOU.

00:11:58,144 --> 00:12:01,314
I'M VERY FRUSTRATED
WITH YOU GUYS, I GOTTA TELL YOU.

00:12:01,314 --> 00:12:04,217
WHY?
I THINK YOU'RE TRYING
TO SELL THE FUTURE

00:12:04,217 --> 00:12:06,753
IN A WAY THAT NO INVESTOR
WOULD PAY FOR.

00:12:06,753 --> 00:12:08,554
THE WORLD'S CHANGED.

00:12:08,554 --> 00:12:12,025
YOU CAN'T GET THAT LOAN
FROM A BANK,

00:12:12,025 --> 00:12:14,694
OR YOU WOULD HAVE DONE IT.
WE BOTH KNOW THAT.

00:12:14,694 --> 00:12:17,630
IT'S A MISSED OPPORTUNITY
FOR YOU... AND FOR ME.

00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:19,132
I'M OUT.

00:12:23,736 --> 00:12:26,272
GOOD LUCK.

00:12:30,710 --> 00:12:34,047
I LIKED IT A LOT.
I LIKED IT A LOT. I REALLY DID.
(Robert) THEY HAVE TO GO
TO THE BANKS.

00:12:34,047 --> 00:12:38,184
IT WAS A GREAT BUSINESS.
THE VALUE WAS CRAZY.
IT WAS A GREAT BUSINESS.

00:12:38,184 --> 00:12:40,520
WITH EVERYTHING THAT WE'VE
PUT INTO THIS COMPANY‐‐

00:12:40,520 --> 00:12:42,522
FIVE YEARS
OF FULL‐TIME DEDICATION

00:12:42,522 --> 00:12:45,024
AND THE FACT THAT WE'VE
ALREADY GOT TEN LOCATIONS‐‐

00:12:45,024 --> 00:12:47,026
AND THEY THINK WE'RE ONLY
WORTH $600,000?

00:12:47,026 --> 00:12:49,028
THEY'RE WAY OFF THE MARK.
IT'S INSANE.

00:12:49,028 --> 00:12:52,398
<i>MONTHS AGO,</i>
<i>WE WATCHED LORI LITE</i>

00:12:52,398 --> 00:12:56,669
<i>SEAL A $250,000 DEAL</i>
<i>WITH BARBARA CORCORAN.</i>

00:12:56,669 --> 00:12:59,505
I THINK WE CAN WORK TOGETHER.
IS THAT A YES?

00:12:59,505 --> 00:13:03,009
I ACCEPT YOUR DEAL.
IT'S A CRAZY DEAL...

00:13:03,009 --> 00:13:05,712
IT'S NOT A CRAZY DEAL AT ALL.
BUT CRAZIER THINGS
HAVE HAPPENED. THANK YOU.

00:13:05,712 --> 00:13:07,680
<i>LET'S SEE WHAT SHE'S UP TO NOW.</i>

00:13:07,680 --> 00:13:10,249
♪♪

00:13:10,249 --> 00:13:12,652
THIS IS A DREAM‐COME‐TRUE DAY
FOR ME.

00:13:12,652 --> 00:13:13,920
I'M HERE AT BORDERS BOOKSTORE

00:13:13,920 --> 00:13:17,256
TO DO A SIGNING AND A READING
OF ONE OF MY BEST‐SELLING BOOKS.

