STRESS FREE KIDS
IS A LINE OF BOOKS AND CDs

00:13:19,993 --> 00:13:22,695
DESIGNED TO HELP CHILDREN
DECREASE STRESS AND ANGER

00:13:22,695 --> 00:13:24,697
WHILE PROMOTING
THEIR SELF‐ESTEEM.

00:13:24,697 --> 00:13:28,201
"SHE PLACED HERSELF ACROSS
FROM THE DOLPHIN AND SAID,

00:13:28,201 --> 00:13:30,203
'I BELIEVE IN MYSELF.'"

00:13:30,203 --> 00:13:33,339
(children and Lori)
I BELIEVE IN MYSELF!

00:13:33,339 --> 00:13:35,475
(Lori)
BUT THE MOST EXCITING NEWS

00:13:35,475 --> 00:13:38,411
IS THAT MY TITLES HAVE BEEN
PICKED UP BY BORDERS

00:13:38,411 --> 00:13:40,546
AND ARE GOING TO BE
IN THEIR STORES NATIONWIDE.

00:13:40,546 --> 00:13:42,548
THIS IS
THE BEST BOOK EVER.

00:13:42,548 --> 00:13:45,018
IT'S THE BEST BOOK EVER?
YEP.

00:13:45,018 --> 00:13:47,687
THE FUTURE IS REALLY BRIGHT
FOR STRESS FREE KIDS.

00:13:47,687 --> 00:13:51,090
WE ARE EXPANDING OUR BRAND,
WE ARE REACHING MORE CHILDREN

00:13:51,090 --> 00:13:53,059
NOT ONLY IN AMERICA,
BUT GLOBALLY.

00:13:53,059 --> 00:13:55,661
HI, HONEY.
I WOULD NOT HAVE GOTTEN
TO THIS PLACE

00:13:55,661 --> 00:13:58,898
THIS FAR THIS FAST
WITHOUT "SHARK TANK."

00:14:10,543 --> 00:14:13,079
♪♪

00:14:13,079 --> 00:14:16,149
<i>NEXT UP ARE MARIX STONE</i>
<i>AND NANCY TANCHEL</i>

00:14:16,149 --> 00:14:18,418
<i>WITH A PRODUCT</i>
<i>DESIGNED TO LOOK COOL</i>

00:14:18,418 --> 00:14:21,054
<i>WHILE KEEPING YOU SAFE.</i>

00:14:26,159 --> 00:14:28,227
HI. I'M MARIX STONE,

00:14:28,227 --> 00:14:31,464
AND I'M THE CREATOR AND DESIGNER
