00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:23,536
YOUR BALL TO ROLL OFF‐LINE.
SO WHAT DO YOU DO?

00:22:23,536 --> 00:22:26,672
GO RIGHT TO YOUR BAG, YOU UNCLIP
YOU PORTABLE GOLF BALL CLEANER

00:22:26,672 --> 00:22:28,874
AND SIMPLY UNSCREW IT.

00:22:28,874 --> 00:22:30,876
YOU TAKE THE BALL
AND YOU PUT IT

00:22:30,876 --> 00:22:33,412
ON THE BOTTOM HALF
FOR THE BRISTLES.

00:22:33,412 --> 00:22:35,848
YOU TAKE THE TOP HALF
AND YOU SCREW IT BACK DOWN.

00:22:35,848 --> 00:22:38,617
YOU GIVE IT A LITTLE SHAKE
AND THEN YOU SIMPLY TWIST

00:22:38,617 --> 00:22:41,554
YOUR TWISTER BACK AND FORTH.
THAT CLEANS IT.

00:22:41,554 --> 00:22:43,422
ONCE YOU'RE DONE
DOING THE TWIST,

00:22:43,422 --> 00:22:45,591
YOU SIMPLY UNSCREW IT
ONCE AGAIN

00:22:45,591 --> 00:22:47,593
AND YOU TAKE OUT A GOLF BALL

00:22:47,593 --> 00:22:50,796
THAT LOOKS LIKE
IT'S BRAND‐NEW AGAIN.

